    "rich_text_hYW86B": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_FytkEb": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "MUMU BATH WHERE CLAY MEETS LUXURY"
          }
        },
        "richtext_AAwXXf": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Discover the Natural Luxury of Clay Soap Bars</h2><p>Experience the pure touch of nature with our handcrafted soaps. Each bar is made with premium clays like French green, pink, and kaolin. These natural clays draw out impurities while keeping your skin soft and hydrated. Perfect for sensitive, oily, or acne-prone skin.</p><p>At Mumu Bath, we believe in simple, clean, and effective skincare. Our soaps are made with plant-based oils and natural ingredients. They are <a>cold-processed</a> in small batches for maximum benefits. A gentle way to care for your skin and the planet.</p><h2>Why Choose Our <strong>Clay Soap Bars</strong>?</h2><ol><li><strong>Mineral-Rich Formulas</strong>: Our clay soaps are packed with essential minerals and elements that work wonders for your skin.</li><li><strong>Detoxifying Power</strong>: Clay naturally draws out toxins and absorbs impurities, leaving your skin refreshed and revitalized.</li><li><strong>Gentle Cleansing</strong>: Experience a deep clean without harsh chemicals or synthetic additives.</li><li><strong>Skin-Softening Effects</strong>: Enjoy softer, more beautiful skin with regular use.</li><li><strong>Essential Oil Infusions</strong>: Our carefully selected essential oils refresh and tone your skin, enhancing the soap's benefits.</li><li><strong>All-Natural Colorants</strong>: The beautiful hues in our soaps come from natural sources like clays and dried powdered herbs.</li></ol><h3>Our Clay Varieties</h3><p>We use a range of micro-pulverized clays in our soaps, each offering unique benefits:</p><p><strong>French Green Clay</strong>: Known for its detoxifying properties</p><p><strong>Rose Pink Clay</strong>: Gentle and soothing for sensitive skin</p><p><strong>Kaolin Clay</strong>: Mild and suitable for all skin types</p><p></p><h2>The Art of Handcrafted Soap Making</h2><p>Our clay soaps are lovingly handcrafted using traditional methods. We take pride in the saponification process, where natural oils and lye combine to create gentle, nourishing soap. Each bar is carefully molded, cut, and cured for several weeks to ensure the highest quality.</p><p><strong>Experience the Difference</strong></p><p>Our clay soap products offer:</p><ul><li>Extra creamy lather for a luxurious bathing experience</li><li>Slicker texture, perfect for use as shaving soap</li><li>Variety in colors, shapes, sizes, and styles</li><li>A simple, natural way to replenish your skin</li></ul><p>Embrace the joy of natural skincare with our Clay Soap collection. Your skin deserves the best – treat it to the purifying power of clay and the nourishing benefits of handcrafted soap.</p><p>Shop our Clay Soap collection now and transform your daily cleansing routine into a spa-like experience!</p><h2>How to Use for Best Results</h2><p><strong> Cleanse Gently - </strong>Lather the <strong>soap clay</strong> with warm water between your<br/>hands. Massage the rich foam onto damp skin, then rinse thoroughly.</p><p><strong>Seal in Moisture - </strong>After drying, apply our Lightweight Body Butter or Body Oil.<br/>This helps lock in hydration and leaves your skin soft and nourished.</p><p><strong>Make It Last - </strong>To prolong the life of your bar, store it <a>on</a> a well-<a>draining</a> soap<br/>dish. Avoid leaving it in standing water between uses.</p><p> </p><h2>Why Shop <a>From</a> Us</h2><p><strong> </strong></p><p><strong>Natural & Thoughtful Ingredients<br/>- </strong>We use high-quality, skin-loving<br/>ingredients in every bar. No harsh chemicals - just clean, conscious care.</p><p><strong>Handcrafted with Purpose - </strong>Each <strong>soap clay</strong> bar is handmade in small batches. This ensures attention to detail and consistent quality.</p><p><strong>Sustainable Packaging - </strong>Our packaging is eco-friendly and minimal. It's better for your skin and the planet.</p><p><strong>Hydration You Can Feel - </strong>Pair our soaps with our body butters or oils for<br/>long-lasting softness. Your skin stays moisturized, smooth, and nourished all<br/>day.</p><p><strong>Trusted by Our Community - </strong>We’ve earned loyal customers who care about clean beauty. Their feedback continues to shape what we create next.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
